data.description: If you are looking for some peaceful country living then this is the place for you. This beautiful residence has been well taken care of and maintained through the years. Located here in Sterling Idaho just down the road from the American Falls Reservoir. As you enter this magnificent home you are greeted with a spacious living area full of natural light to brighten up each day. The master suite is vast with vaulted ceilings, a spacious walk in closet, and a private bathroom that includes a stand-up shower/soaker tub. As for the spacious kitchen it's very well laid out with a breakfast bar and ample storage space with the pantry/cupboards. The laundry room is located right next to the kitchen with extra storage area for your convenience. Then you have sliding doors off the dining area that leads to the back patio opening the perfect opportunity to do some good old fashion barbequing year round. Just off the main living area opens up to a spacious family room with large windows overlooking the backyard giving you a front row seat to the beautiful scenery of Idaho country. With two more bedrooms perfect for guests/children and a bathroom you have a complete home of your dreams. The yard is well established with mature trees, flower beds, and a gardening area. Come take a look!!!
